{"word":"τρέχω","slug":"τρέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>τρέχω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τροχός\">τροχός</a></el>] ‘move forward rapidly’, <b>run<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of physical motion <b><a href='B:470 27:48'>Mt 27:48</a>; <a href='B:480 5:6'>Mk 5:6</a>; <a href='B:490 15:20'>Lk 15:20</a>; <a href='B:500 20:2'>J 20:2</a>, <a href='B:500 20:4'>4</a>; <a href='B:530 9:24'>1 Cor 9:24</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ metaph.\">metaph.</a> <b><a href='B:520 9:16'>Ro 9:16</a>; <a href='B:530 9:26'>1 Cor 9:26</a>; <a href='B:550 2:2'>Gal 2:2</a>; <a href='B:550 5:7'>5:7</a>; <a href='B:570 2:16'>Phil 2:16</a>; <a href='B:650 12:1'>Hb 12:1</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἵνα\">ἵνα</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λόγος\">λόγος</a> τοῦ Κυρίου τρέχῃ</el> that the Lord’s message might make fast progress <b><a href='B:600 3:1'>2 Th 3:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:τρέφω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:τρῆμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}